com.example.link.appfuzzer

Class Configuration

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.link.appfuzzer.Configuration

  • public class Configuration
extends java.lang.Object
    This class holds information over the behavior of AppFuzzer. Many of its values are set through the intent from the wrapper script.
